{"text_id":107047,"tokens":["Analysis"," of"," opinion"," dynamics"," in"," social"," networks"," plays"," an"," important"," role"," in"," today","'","s"," life","."," For"," applications"," such"," as"," predicting"," users","'"," political"," preference",","," it"," is"," particularly"," important"," to"," be"," able"," to"," detect"," the"," existence"," of"," influential"," individuals",","," that"," is",","," individuals"," who"," can"," affect"," others","'"," opinions"," more"," than"," others"," do","."," The"," key"," question"," in"," this"," paper"," is",":"," can"," we"," characterize"," the"," influential"," individuals"," in"," social"," networks","?"," In"," the"," social"," network",","," the"," nodes"," represent"," individuals"," and"," the"," links"," represent"," their"," relationships","."," The"," influential"," individuals"," are"," the"," nodes"," that"," have"," larger"," weights"," of"," influence"," than"," others"," do","."," The"," weights"," of"," influence"," represent"," the"," extent"," to"," which"," they"," can"," affect"," others","'"," opinions","."," Therefore",","," the"," influence"," of"," a"," node"," is"," a"," function"," of"," the"," number"," of"," nodes"," to"," which"," it"," is"," connected",","," the"," weight"," of"," influence"," of"," the"," node",","," and"," the"," strength"," of"," the"," node","."," In"," this"," paper",","," we"," study"," the"," problem"," of"," influence"," maximization"," (","IM",")"," and"," propose"," a"," Normalized"," Entropy"," Based"," method"," to"," maximize"," the"," total"," weight"," of"," influence","."," The"," entropy"," is"," defined"," as"," the"," logarithm"," of"," the"," sum"," of"," the"," probabilities"," of"," all"," the"," possible"," states"," of"," a"," system","."," We"," show"," that"," this"," method"," can"," find"," the"," influential"," individuals"," in"," a"," network"," with"," the"," optimal"," time"," complexity","."," Furthermore",","," we"," show"," that"," the"," optimal"," solution"," can"," be"," achieved"," by"," an"," online"," algorithm",","," which"," is"," the"," first"," online"," algorithm"," for"," the"," problem","."," Experimental"," results"," show"," that"," our"," method"," can"," find"," the"," influential"," individuals"," with"," the"," same"," accuracy"," as"," the"," best"," offline"," algorithm","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"GLM130B","label":1}